{
  "stem": "471.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was, at that time, at the hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the whole hospital-- with the doctors and the nurses, with everybody, they rounded up the hospital, and they-- they took them to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And now, [NON-ENGLISH] is a big-- is a big no.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Marketplace.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Over there, they were-- they were standing with a machine gun, and they were killing them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my father was shot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother and my sister, they were sent to Belzec, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They killed them in Belzec.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know, from those days, because I was up there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I knew, so what will happen?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It will be more tragic for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The condition of Plaszow, by God, was unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] How unbelievable that you can see-- if you see-- if you see the movie you know, it's too hard to describe.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, you can't-- if you live a story, you can't put on a paper everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can't write on a paper everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe while I'm talking to you, maybe I will-- maybe we'll-- my computer will set it back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is-- there is-- there is no-- you can't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's almost unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I made a statement like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, you write a story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You can't-- the paper-- you can't write everything on your paper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of things.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I tell you the truth, if I were-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [GROANS] My personal friend-- I showed a picture from him with you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to watch him, the way they hanged him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The way they hanged them, two of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From one, I have, still, a picture from before the war, which I will show you later.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other one, I didn't have a picture.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
